o much out of him as you're taking away as you'm getting now. 'Cos he said we're on government work. So, he said, well - the point is he isn't working full time on agricultural machinery. But he said, that isn't for me to decide. He said that's up for the
 
committee. But he said - it meant if I had to go I should have to go to - Asked for me again. So I said to the manager I said well look Mr Chace, the best thing I can do is start in business on me own. So, he said, well do you think you've got enough, wel
