 Lord Churston when I applied for it they told me they said, well we know you can handle the place, your name been mentioned many time. But it wasn't our place to approach you, but now you've approached us - and they said, what we're concerned about it - 
i
t's an estate blacksmith's shop, and it's our duty to look after our customers, our - our own tenants, and he said - Mr Ecks have told us about you and he said and other people. So he said, there's no doubt about it, we know you'm the man for the place, h
