Oh well just a - social gathering you know and make our own sort of fun. And sometimes if it was a special occasion get outsiders, but - very very seldom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5273668 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Were there many garden fetes and things like that?
