\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5273668 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Did your mother have many interests outside the home? You say she was a member of the Band of Hope?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16138623 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Well, in those days of course there - there - there wasn't so many so - social functions like the women}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15931879\charrsid11994791 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 s institution and all that sort of thing as there is -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5273668 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Was there a mothers union or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16138623 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 No, no such thing in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5273668 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16138623 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Oh not very much, only when - when father -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5273668 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 When did your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16138623 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Oh good lor' he was working from daylight 'til dark. Couldn't get out later than that, some - he was - well I did in the early days,
 I was out soon as it was day - light and wouldn't -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5273668 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 When did your father die, what year was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16138623 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Oh now, I'm afraid you've got me there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5273668 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Very recently was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16138623 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Oh no, several year ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5273668 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 In the 1950's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16138623 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Oh, later than that. Or earlier than that, wait a minute, 72 now isn't it? I should say somewhere about - about 62 or 3.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5273668 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 And your mother died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16138623 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Oh she died many years ago. Yes, mother's been gone many year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5273668 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Who would say grace at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16138623 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Oh father of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5273668 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 What age were you when you were first able to put yourself to bed do you think?
