\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5273668 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Who organised the family prayers, was that your father and your mother?
