nd - that would be that. They wouldn't dream of touching of 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5273668 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 What would they expect you to do, just leave them alone or hit them back?
