\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5273668 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14307531\charrsid11994791 Did he go to meetings and things like that?
