k road, you got to be so many away - so many feet away from a trunk road, otherwise - it's got to - definitely got to go planning. So I said, well - I knew that in me mind and you must have know. Well he said, that's quite true. But he said I did think th
at - planning - representative Devon Country would have said well it's a replacement and - we won't quibble about it, but he said it's not so. So he said, to save time we }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15931879\charrsid11994791 
